trans-unit.source: An abstract base class that encapsulates functionality that is common to file dialogs, including <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref> and <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En abstrakt basisklasse som innkapsler funksjonalitet som er felles for filen ovenfor, inkludert <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref> og <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether a file dialog automatically adds an extension to a file name if the user omits an extension.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om dialogboksen automatisk legger til en type i et filnavn Hvis brukeren utelater filtypen.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if extensions are added; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis utvidelser er lagt til; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether a file dialog displays a warning if the user specifies a file name that does not exist.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om dialogboksen viser en advarsel hvis brukeren angir et navn som ikke finnes.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog> class sets this property to `true` in its constructor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog>klasse, settes egenskapen til `true` i sin konstruktør.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if warnings are displayed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis advarsler vises; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default in this base class is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard i denne basisklassen er <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether warnings are displayed if the user types invalid paths and file names.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om varsler vises hvis brukeren skriver ugyldig baner og filnavn.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if warnings are displayed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis advarsler vises; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the list of custom places for file dialog boxes.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir listen over egendefinerte steder for dialogbokser.

trans-unit.source: Starting in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winvista](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winvista-md.md)], open and save file dialog boxes have a **Favorite Links** panel on the left side of the dialog box that allows the user to quickly navigate to a different location.
trans-unit.target: Starter i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winvista](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winvista-md.md)]ved å åpne og lagre dialogbokser har en **koblinger** panelet til venstre i dialogboksen som gir brukeren mulighet til å navigere raskt til en annen plassering.

trans-unit.source: These links are called custom places.
trans-unit.target: Disse koblingene kalles egendefinerte steder.

trans-unit.source: This property allows you to modify the list that appears when your application uses a file dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan du endre listen som vises når programmet bruker en dialogboks.

trans-unit.source: The list of custom places.
trans-unit.target: Listen over egendefinerte steder.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies the default extension string to use to filter the list of files that are displayed.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir standard utvidelsesstrengen som skal brukes til å filtrere listen over filer som skal vises.

trans-unit.source: The extension string must contain the leading period.
trans-unit.target: Utvidelsesstrengen må inneholde innledende punktum.

trans-unit.source: For example, set the DefaultExt property to ".txt" to select all text files.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel ikke angi egenskapen DefaultExt til "txt" for å velge alle text-filer.

trans-unit.source: By default, the <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.AddExtension%2A> property attempts to determine the extension to filter the displayed file list from the <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.Filter%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Som standard i <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.AddExtension%2A>egenskapen prøver å finne forlengelse for å filtrere listen over viste filer fra de <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.Filter%2A>egenskapen.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.Filter%2A> </xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.AddExtension%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the extension cannot be determined from the <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.Filter%2A> property, DefaultExt will be used instead.
trans-unit.target: Hvis utvidelsen ikke kan fastslås fra den <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.Filter%2A>, DefaultExt skal brukes i stedet.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.Filter%2A>

trans-unit.source: The default extension string.
trans-unit.target: Standard utvidelsesstrengen.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: Standard er <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether a file dialog returns either the location of the file referenced by a shortcut or the location of the shortcut file (.lnk).
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om dialogboksen returnerer plasseringen av filen refererer til en snarvei eller plasseringen av snarveifilen (lnk).

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to return the location referenced; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to return the shortcut location.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Returnerer plasseringen refererer til; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> til å returnere snarvei plasseringen.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a string containing the full path of the file selected in a file dialog.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en streng som inneholder den fullstendige banen til filen valgte i dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: If more than one file name is selected (length of <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileNames%2A> is greater than one) then FileName contains the first selected file name.
trans-unit.target: Hvis mer enn én filnavn velges (lengden på <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileNames%2A>er større enn én) og filnavnet inneholder det første valgte filnavnet.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileNames%2A>

trans-unit.source: If no file name is selected, this property contains <xref:System.String.Empty> rather than `null`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen filnavn er merket, inneholder denne egenskapen <xref:System.String.Empty>snarere enn `null`.</xref:System.String.Empty>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that is the full path of the file selected in the file dialog.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som den fullstendige banen til filen valgte i dialogboksen filen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: Standard er <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets an array that contains one file name for each selected file.
trans-unit.target: Henter en matrise som inneholder ett navn for hver fil som er valgt.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.String> that contains one file name for each selected file.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref:System.String>som inneholder ett navn for hver fil som er valgt.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: The default is an array with a single item whose value is <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: Standard er en matrise med ett enkelt element med en verdi er <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Occurs when the user selects a file name by either clicking the **Open** button of the <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref> or the **Save** button of the <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når brukeren velger et filnavn ved enten å klikke den **åpne** knappen av den <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref> eller **lagre** knapp for den <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: FileOk is raised after the user selects a file name, but before the dialog closes, which allows you to process the selection.
trans-unit.target: FileOk oppstår etter at brukeren velger et filnavn, men før dialogboksen lukkes, slik at du kan behandle utvalget.

trans-unit.source: If required, the user's selection can be cancelled by setting the <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs> argument to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Om nødvendig brukerens valg kan avbrytes ved å angi den <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>-egenskapen til det <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs>argumentet til `true`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs> </xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the filter string that determines what types of files are displayed from either the <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref> or <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir Filterstrengen som avgjør hvilke filtyper som vises fra enten den <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref> eller <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the filter.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder filteret.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref:System.String>, which means that no filter is applied and all file types are displayed.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref:System.String>, noe som betyr at ingen filteret, og alle filtyper vises.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: The filter string is invalid.
trans-unit.target: Filterstrengen er ugyldig.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the index of the filter currently selected in a file dialog.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir indeksen for filteret som er valgt i dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: This index is 1-based, not 0-based, due to compatibility requirements with the underlying [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-win32-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_api](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-api-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Denne indeksen er basert på 1, ikke 0-basert, på grunn av kravene for kompatibilitet med den underliggende [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-win32-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_api](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-api-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Int32> that is the index of the selected filter.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Int32>som indeksen for det valgte filteret.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: The default is 1.
trans-unit.target: Standard er 1.

trans-unit.source: Defines the common file dialog hook procedure that is overridden to add common functionality to a file dialog.
trans-unit.target: Definerer vanlige filen dialogboksen binding fremgangsmåten som overstyres for å legge til felles funksjonalitet dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: Window handle for the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-win32-md.md)] dialog.
trans-unit.target: Vindusreferansen for den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-win32-md.md)] dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: Message to be processed by the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-win32-md.md)] dialog.
trans-unit.target: Meldingen som skal behandles av den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-win32-md.md)] dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: Parameters for dialog actions.
trans-unit.target: Parametere for dialogboksen handlinger.

trans-unit.source: Parameters for dialog actions.
trans-unit.target: Parametere for dialogboksen handlinger.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.IntPtr> to indicate success; otherwise, a non-zero value is returned to indicate failure.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer <xref:System.IntPtr>som viser vellykket; ellers returneres en ikke-null-verdi som viser feil.</xref:System.IntPtr>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the initial directory that is displayed by a file dialog.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den første katalogen som vises av dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: If there is no initial directory set, this property will contain <xref:System.String> rather than a null string.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er ingen opprinnelig mappe er angitt, denne egenskapen vil inneholde <xref:System.String>i stedet for en nullstreng.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the initial directory.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder den opprinnelige katalogen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: Standard er <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Raises the <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileOk"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Hever den <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileOk"> </xref> hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: OnFileOk raises the <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileOk> event.
trans-unit.target: Opphøyer OnFileOk den <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileOk>hendelsen.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileOk>

trans-unit.source: A type that derives from <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog> may override OnFileOk.
trans-unit.target: En type som er avledet fra <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog>kan overstyre OnFileOk.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog>

trans-unit.source: The overridden method must call OnFileOk on the base class if <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileOk> needs to be raised.
trans-unit.target: Metoden overstyrte må ringe OnFileOk på basisklassen <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileOk>må oppstå.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileOk>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs> that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs>som inneholder Hendelsesdata.</xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-win32-md.md)] common file dialog flags that are used by file dialogs for initialization.
trans-unit.target: Henter den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-win32-md.md)] vanlige filen dialogboksen flaggene som brukes av filen dialogbokser for initialisering.

trans-unit.source: This value is used to display a file dialog with the current set of property values.
trans-unit.target: Denne verdien brukes til å vise dialogboksen med gjeldende sett med verdier.

trans-unit.source: The actual options are exposed as properties on the specific dialogs, but not documented as public flag values at this level, so the uses of this property are mainly internal, for use when implementing the derived classes <xref:Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog> and <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog>.
trans-unit.target: Alternativene faktiske eksponert som egenskaper på bestemte ovenfor, men ikke dokumentert som offentlig flaggverdier på dette nivået og bruk av denne egenskapen er hovedsakelig interne, for bruk når implementering av avledede klasser <xref:Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog>og <xref:Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog>.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog> </xref:Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Int32> that contains the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-win32-md.md)] common file dialog flags that are used by file dialogs for initialization.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Int32>som inneholder den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-win32-md.md)] vanlige filen dialogboksen flaggene som brukes av filen dialogbokser for initialisering.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Sets all properties of a file dialog back to their initial values.
trans-unit.target: Angir alle egenskaper av dialogboksen tilbake til sin opprinnelige verdier.

trans-unit.source: This property is not implemented.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er ikke implementert.

trans-unit.source: Not implemented.
trans-unit.target: Ikke implementert.

trans-unit.source: <xref:Microsoft.Win32.CommonDialog.RunDialog*> is called to display a file dialog in a derived class, such as <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref> and <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Win32.CommonDialog.RunDialog*>kalles for å vise dialogboksen i en avledet klasse eksempel <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref> og <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"> </xref>.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.CommonDialog.RunDialog*>

trans-unit.source: The dialog that is eventually shown is assigned an owner window, which is specified by the `hwndOwner` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Dialogboksen oppgavestatusen vises er tilordnet en eiervinduet, som er angitt i den `hwndOwner` parameteren.

trans-unit.source: Handle to the window that owns the dialog.
trans-unit.target: Behandle til vinduet som eier dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the user clicks the **OK** button of the dialog that is displayed (for example, <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref>, <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"></xref>); otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis brukeren velger den **OK** for dialogboksen vises (for eksempel <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref>, <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"> </xref>); ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a string that only contains the file name for the selected file.
trans-unit.target: Henter en streng som inneholder bare filnavnet for den valgte filen.

trans-unit.source: This value is the <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileName%2A> with all path information removed.
trans-unit.target: Denne verdien er den <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileName%2A>med alle baneinformasjon fjernet.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.FileName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Removing the paths makes the value appropriate for use in partial trust applications, since it prevents applications from discovering information about the local file system.
trans-unit.target: Fjerne banene er verdien som brukes i delvis klarering programmer, fordi den forhindrer programmer fra å oppdage informasjon om det lokale filsystemet.

trans-unit.source: If more than one file name is selected (length of <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.SafeFileNames%2A> is greater than one) then this property contains only the first selected file name.
trans-unit.target: Hvis mer enn én filnavn velges (lengden på <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.SafeFileNames%2A>er større enn én) og deretter denne egenskapen inneholder bare det første merkede filnavnet.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.SafeFileNames%2A>

trans-unit.source: See [Safe File Upload from an XBAP Sample](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01206dd3-acc7-45ff-aeb9-502c20aaad2c).
trans-unit.target: Se [trygg filopplasting fra en XBAP eksempel](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01206dd3-acc7-45ff-aeb9-502c20aaad2c).

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that only contains the file name for the selected file.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som bare inneholder filnavn for den valgte filen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref:System.String>, which is also the value when either no file is selected or a directory is selected.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref:System.String>, som er også verdien at ingen filer er valgt, eller en katalog er valgt.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets an array that contains one safe file name for each selected file.
trans-unit.target: Henter en matrise som inneholder navnet på en trygg fil for hver fil som er valgt.

trans-unit.source: See <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.SafeFileName%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Se <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.SafeFileName%2A>.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.SafeFileName%2A>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.String> that contains one safe file name for each selected file.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref:System.String>som inneholder navnet på en trygg fil for hver fil som er valgt.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: The default is an array with a single item whose value is <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: Standard er en matrise med ett enkelt element med en verdi er <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the text that appears in the title bar of a file dialog.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir teksten som vises i tittellinjen i dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: If Title is null or <xref:System.String>, a default, localized value is used, such as "Save As" or "Open".
trans-unit.target: Hvis tittelen er null eller <xref:System.String>, standard oversatte verdien brukes, slik som "Lagre som" eller "Åpne".</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that is the text that appears in the title bar of a file dialog.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som tekst som vises i tittellinjen i dialogboksen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: Standard er <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Returns a string that represents a file dialog.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en streng som representerer en dialogboks i filen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> representation of <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog"></xref> that contains the full pathname for any files selected from either <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref>, <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>representasjon av <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog"> </xref> som inneholder det fullstendige banenavnet for alle filer som er valgt fra enten <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref>, <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.SaveFileDialog"> </xref>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the dialog accepts only valid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-win32-md.md)] file names.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om dialogboksen godtar bare gyldig [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_win32](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-win32-md.md)] filnavn.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if warnings will be shown when an invalid file name is provided; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis advarsler som skal vises når et ugyldig filnavn er angitt; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
